{
  "id": "RAW_03e28d",
  "title": "用手机发邮件，即可让 Claude Code 干活！无需电脑、无需服务器、甚至无需科学上网！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247498734&idx=1&sn=ec922029a3275bb70ddfdc2405efa9b2",
  "date": "2025-08-30 10:20:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color: inherit; font-size: 1rem;\">大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你知道吗，现在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">我们只需要写个邮件，就能让Claude Code干活。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">邮件可用手机写，全程不打开电脑，甚至不用打开科学上网。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code干完活后，会通过邮件告诉我，并且把所有干活的过程和结果记录下来，随时可查。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如下图所示</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">演示</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">图1： 躺床上，拿出手机，慵懒的用QQ邮箱，给Claude Code布置任务</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015066\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0641975308641975\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"810\" style=\"width: 428px;height: 455px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=beeb65fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmsL7TsAbpqYqPibldmPvQFyib607k6FeufencmzjYDhsDlOlhiceRapDWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">图2：Claude Code 干完任务后，通过QQ邮箱，告诉我进度、留下了检验工作内容的链接。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015067\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.183333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 232px;height: 507px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=138a4b45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfm5Xaq0HIDcmGxthvJoKSribRDhGVHzULvp7pqlGjB19X5N4hicaLGQQXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">图3：我可以点击链接，查看它的工作过程、验收工作进度</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015068\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.4546296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0d0f4d8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfm4mUThCnesNp6vCy8wtlJphASLG3HO9eT7VEgV4IEBpkAbicQUgqPyow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">想学吗？&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">往下看！！</span></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">原理</span></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么这么神奇？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">原理上不复杂： &nbsp;Claude Code 有一个鲜为人知的功能—— &nbsp;Claude Code Github Actions。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">按照官方的说法：&nbsp;</span></p>\n    <blockquote>\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">只需在任何 PR 或 issue 中简单地提及 @claude，Claude 就可以分析您的代码、创建拉取请求、实现功能和修复错误 - 所有这些都遵循您项目的标准。</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">我们可以翻译为人话： &nbsp;配置成功后，我通过任何方式（包括邮件）在Github的issue中输入 @claude ，就可以给Claude Code布置任务了。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015071\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd35d1a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmuvsLP88aeJwAibvE0mDAhm30WgSYeSDZv7FdsqR7dfYhbAXOG2AHbbA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体怎么配置？</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">配置方法</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">很简单！几乎全自动！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">打开Claude Code, 输入&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">/install-github-app</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015047\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41388888888888886\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a5e215a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmicYk0R2ruibgNZ8pzBrzgZKecD27NQnicB8ncNMkPqGuCMcloTib96yiaqQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">跟着提示往下进行即可。&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面以我的项目 Raphael AI ( 产品网址 <a href=\"https://raphael.app\" target=\"_blank\">https://raphael.app</a> ) 为例，向大家演示配置过程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你可以对照我下文的截图。每个步骤，我都截图了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015049\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.37861915367483295\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"898\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fb4bf065&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmYo1BkTK55x4YnNaT11tialUSOR1sDPuuWLXKgXiaghzrzjgrHkicLXMUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015050\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4537037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ce2c3bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmSkHRcnkcNmY4okJJsdiaN3iamFvKgPcBkmntHJLvCPUThrCxllPp5lgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里，需要登录的时候，记得选择</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style:italic;\">Create a long-lived toekn with your Claude Subscription</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015051\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3797216699801193\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1006\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bad722f4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmFqoKIKkqGGn8HP4AfIhTvoGdcMXlUoYXOtOPMNr4SCPj8Ez3UL5d0A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015052\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48031496062992124\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"762\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=497c3b32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfmsuymf5CCoEibiaBRBm96m5Lrib2v3kpibvcUVanPrO1lC0PeibMBZj5xkjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015053\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47959183673469385\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"980\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=45fd4816&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmqoWvEkL2awEDdMUOZ7Q8lic0QTYrRrKBsDl1Tfbs7SffgGvlZicFnsSA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015054\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2212962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9d5fef6d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmhNa1bzMBwMjLMpaicyMax7wOMLycc2EfaZvj3lpPsXfnb0MJfQj9BLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">配置完成了，Claude Code 会自动为你在Github上创建一个PR。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你想探究细节，可以仔细阅读。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你只是快速配置，这里直接点击“<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">Merge Pull Request</span>”就好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015055\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.575\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0923c4d4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmQHYyslbb3DDtMPnuCTpuVDicBeCylsxicHiaFMg0tjvK8Z2F0hBhww5bw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015057\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8722222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87e7684e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmWTFhsSYpqVBIVXic6HZpSXpNkBibqvITfN2zTZkJDicGIdeMh7EMfWZPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">使用方法-基础</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">打开Github的Issues，随便写点啥。只要你输入了 @claude， &nbsp;Claude Code就会干活。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">下面的例子中，我输入了</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">@claude 这个项目一共有多少行代码？</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015058\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=864fddb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfm22KtxX9nt0H3miav7chjoodtGs7pOOjwvVWj4evR6VqZMDu0OS3hNtg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">详细截图</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015059\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd3d59f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfm2Cictz45vfsl6RPYKunI6hGQY9SP90SgVJELSq2Zvh1DzAJLeVhoIIQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015060\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8083333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=deb14ac4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmnDOZAJRwrnpTFOJeH8kHJqGyfsdlx2qibyCVlROxMpQwly7jr4oEt6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面是Claude Code的完整输出。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015061\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7611111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 442px;height: 336px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac42f5c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmTMcSic4kP5g0pp8BrIX7AKtsoE3EdOjiaGFv8HeFBx3rrEHNqloyyU0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">使用方法-邮件</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">说好的邮件呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">嗯，别急。既然原理是Github Issue， 我们有很多方式把它变成邮件。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">最简单的方式是 —— 点击 Watch， 选择 Watch All Activity</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015072\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3314814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0679e0a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmGNwBMup2D2zrHQIzbzFhxHXWUjW3VkE3M4GJkaJmzVJKnetXq1gnrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样，所有的issue，都会邮件通知你。</span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如下图所示</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015063\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2222222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 307px;height: 682px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=42aa58e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfmy2iaD6cE3XupDcV2e2EOvW0fNZcEM2lRC2ntq5RaY5ia3QOuqiaIVGkeg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我也可以直接<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);text-decoration: underline;\">回复</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">邮件</span>，为Claude Code布置新任务。正如文章开头的图。<span textstyle=\"\">别忘了：需要 @claude&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015066\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0641975308641975\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"810\" style=\"width: 428px;height: 455px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=beeb65fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmsL7TsAbpqYqPibldmPvQFyib607k6FeufencmzjYDhsDlOlhiceRapDWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以看到，Claude Code一如既往稳定发挥：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015064\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6900c4c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfm2ewlzibDAjzQeibIaibFE9VH5Q6GfRdvkBzjKicucdVgpvhB5niaKN9RjHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015065\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b6eac05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmrXnCJsV0d1tU1zNU0G2wH4UJ0H8lbF19mm970mBeUfUaXwArszhaVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">进阶：为Github Actions中的Claude Code配置最大权限</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">默认配置到Github Actions中的Claude Code只拥有普通权限。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">如何让它拥有最大权限，包括MCP、网络等等？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">当然是用我们的老方法，让它自己看文档！！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">构造Prompt如下，请点开看截图</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n   <li></li>\n  </ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">我当前项目中,为Github Actions中的 claude code 配置这个重要参数: --dangerously-skip-permissions</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">我需要你查看官方文档和上网搜索，仔细研究怎么做，让我们的Claude Code使用最新的Opus 4.1模型、拥有有最大权限</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.anthropic.com/zh-CN/docs/claude-code/github-actions\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.anthropic.com/zh-CN/docs/claude-code/github-actions</a><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-claude-args</span></span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015069\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4305555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7489d65&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmbeXMbT9BtDEJicS28vrokib2IO33eybib035WYvLqRl2Zktuib8OpgXwXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015082\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5925925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4709575e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfmic7sY4CxJ07ibQ56useuaibQQicLhXEzIRrLhibYq1wFOYPIxIfcXnvT8Fw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">查看代码变更，最关键的更改是 claude_args 参数，</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">上面这通操作， 我们实际上修改了：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">提前授予一切权限</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型改成最新的Opus 4.1</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">允许使用所有工具</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">单次最大对话里轮次为50轮</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015081\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29236499068901306\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1074\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1cee9052&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmmfWWonjSRTCncEEJOkQ6lSpF1ZMibVv3gibwFK0d7g7tDa3Zgqa6Tr9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">开始测试</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015079\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7210401891252955\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1692\" style=\"width: 467px;height: 337px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4ea2705&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmIcpKoyGJWoF6wcsaianCgmUrhYpU8ouicvHD56YlqGUWibPJTkZhtP4pQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次接到任务后的Claude Code，它的眼神都变化了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">注意下面红框的内容：&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">它正在用最大权限模式(Run Claude Code with Maximum Permissions)运行</span>！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015076\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7a66c62&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42TfmCnXVFJne1r5MUqhb3T1SH9JFMQAFHCyRDlSvJlO3QicwUyGYa84SicMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">测试高级权限是否配置成功：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们可以给一些<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">明显需要调用外部工具的任务</span>，来确保我们已经配置成功。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">@claude 我需要你到 <a href=\"https://pagespeed.web.dev/\" target=\"_blank\">https://pagespeed.web.dev/</a> 实际测试我们项目的正式环境<a href=\"https://raphael.app\" target=\"_blank\">https://raphael.app</a> 的SEO得分</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你没有配置成功，应该会出现“执行失败”，因为它默认没有调用网络等高级权限。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我这里是执行成功了</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015085\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8287037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9a427dbf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFmpYiacErCLyBjJM6ia42Tfmibb0NPlic6FbKfBaqxtpChlbmyIc6Tiar0fRCLmyzp5BodeYh9vP0eIQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 76, 0);font-size:24px;\">进阶：真实生产力场景</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">上面的演示，多为娱乐场景。事实上，它也是可以用到真实生产力场景的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">例如</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">1. 当我只有手机的时候，想到了一个功能。 我通过语音输入描述需求，通知Claude Code完成任务，并且部署到测试环境，供你验证。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">2. 每次提交代码，都让Claude Code自动做代码审核。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">3. 让Claude Code自动根据代码更改，完成Change Log</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">4. 让Claude Code 帮我写博客（我很多项目里的博客都是mdx格式文件，在这种情况下，一篇博客，b本质上是一种=段代码）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">5. 当我只有手机的时候，也想要和Claude Code基于我的项目，讨论技术方案</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">……</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">是不是特别有趣？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你还发现了什么有趣的场景、或者生产力场景吗？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">期待你的使用反馈，我们一起交流！ 😄</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
